name: mmmpie
body:
### Practice Writing
I know that I need to practice writing. Since I graduated college I havent really written anything of significant length. A couple of reports and proposals, but I doubt Ive even managed one a year over the last fifteen years. It is time to change that. Even if these posts are hardly longer than a tweet it is a start.
